column5: Any reports from that area in the early season??????
I wish I had one to give but we didn't go up for the opener this year. We leave for Pash. in just over 2 weeks and hopefully a trip to Horseshoe later in the summer.
I ra into problems also--one guy had back surgery and didn't come along very well. I guess I need a few more friends. I hit ya with a personal--hope to hear from you. len
